  <h1>
   draw_get_lighting
  </h1>
  This function will return whether lighting is enabled (
  <span>
   true
  </span>
  ) or not (
  <span>
   false
  </span>
  ) for the whole scene.
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">draw_get_lighting()
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml"><a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Data_Types.htm">
 Boolean
</a></code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">if !draw_get_lighting()
{
    draw_set_lighting(true);
}
</code></pre>
  The above code will check to see if lighting is enabled for the scene, and if not it enables it.
 </body>
